dct_title_s: Map of a portion of the Pymatuning Creek Basin and Yankee Creek Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources.  Pymatuning Creek Basin and Yankee Creek Basin
dct_description_sm: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Pymatuning Creek Basin and Yankee Creek Basin and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower right corner of map.
